summary:
I’m loving every single actor that played the Doctor so far 
Like damn they’re all amazing 
I just can’t explain my feelings...
body:
I’m loving every single actor that played the Doctor so far

Like damn they’re all amazing


I just can’t explain my feelings right now…

Like I feel in love with Christopher and Billie, they were fire and I don’t know you but I’m really falling for the actor at the very beginning of a show or I just don’t like the show!

AND THEN WOAW they’re changing the actor I totally did not expect something like that it was a choc I didn’t wanted them to change AND BAM DAVID TENNANT 😩😩

Like I had no other choices but fall again!!

He’s majestic and what I read about him, he wanted to be the doctor since he was 3 😭😭

Just perfect

And Matt Smith, it’s the same again, no don’t change my Doctor but BAM another incredible actor who just give his best to be a great Doctor and it works…..

Damn it I love that show
